<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Golang on Notebook</title><link>https://ryanpenn.github.io/notebook/tags/golang/</link><description>Recent content in Golang on Notebook</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 14:42:23 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ryanpenn.github.io/notebook/tags/golang/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Ebitengine] (二) API手册</title><link>https://ryanpenn.github.io/notebook/posts/ebitengine/ebiten-2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 14:42:23 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ryanpenn.github.io/notebook/posts/ebitengine/ebiten-2/</guid><description>介绍 &lt;code>Ebiten&lt;/code> 的基本 API。完整的API列表请参见 &lt;a href="https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/hajimehoshi/ebiten/v2">API参考&lt;/a>.</description></item><item><title>[Ebitengine] (一) 简介</title><link>https://ryanpenn.github.io/notebook/posts/ebitengine/ebiten-1/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 21:27:18 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ryanpenn.github.io/notebook/posts/ebitengine/ebiten-1/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="引擎简介">引擎简介&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://ebitengine.org/">Ebitengine&lt;/a> 是一款&lt;a href="https://github.com/hajimehoshi/ebiten">开源&lt;/a>的游戏引擎，基于 Go 语言开发，支持 Windows、Mac、Linux 等平台。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>ebiten 的 API 设计比较简单，使用也很方便，即使对于新手也可以在 1-2 个小时内掌握，并开发出一款简单的游戏。更妙的是，Go 语言让 ebitengine 实现了跨平台！&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="安装">安装&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ebitengine 要求 Go 版本 &amp;gt;= 1.15。使用 go module 下载这个包：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>go get -u github.com/hajimehoshi/ebiten/v2
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="生成游戏窗口">生成游戏窗口&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">package&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">main&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">import&lt;/span> (
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;github.com/hajimehoshi/ebiten/v2&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;github.com/hajimehoshi/ebiten/v2/ebitenutil&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">type&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Game&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">struct&lt;/span>{}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">func&lt;/span> (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">g&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">*&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Game&lt;/span>) &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Update&lt;/span>() &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">error&lt;/span> {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">return&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">nil&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">func&lt;/span> (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">g&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">*&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Game&lt;/span>) &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Draw&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">screen&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">*&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">ebiten&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Image&lt;/span>) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">ebitenutil&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">DebugPrint&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">screen&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Hello, World&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">func&lt;/span> (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">g&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">*&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Game&lt;/span>) &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Layout&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">outsideWidth&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">outsideHeight&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">int&lt;/span>) (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">screenWidth&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">screenHeight&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">int&lt;/span>) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">return&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">200&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">200&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">func&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">main&lt;/span>() {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">ebiten&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">SetWindowSize&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">200&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">200&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">ebiten&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">SetWindowTitle&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;游戏窗口&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">if&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">err&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">:=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">ebiten&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">RunGame&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;amp;&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Game&lt;/span>{}); &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">err&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">!=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">nil&lt;/span> {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">log&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Fatal&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">err&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>运行这个程序，会弹出一个窗口，标题为“生成游戏窗口”，窗口大小为 200x200，并显示“Hello, World”字样。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>